column26: sponsorEmail: Dear XXX,  I hope this email finds you well. My name is Yuqi Wang, and I am the finance associate at Electrium Mobility, which is a student design team at the University of Waterloo. I am writing to you today on behalf of the team to inquire about the possibility of obtaining your support and endorsement as one of our sponsors.  Electrium Mobility is a student design team at the University of Waterloo dedicated to building sustainable, portable, and electric transportation solutions in the form of electric skateboards, bikes, scooters, and other portable electric mobility options. The team currently holds competitions where multiple sub-teams and the University of Waterloo community test and compete with the personal electric vehicles they have built.  As we strive to continue our mission, we are seeking sponsors who share our passion for sustainability and affordable transportation, and are willing to support our efforts in making a positive impact on the student community. This is our fourth official term as a design team, so your support would help us kickstart our activities and allow our members to grow as Engineers! Your support will not only help us advance our mission for sustainable engineering but also demonstrate your dedication to encouraging learning and innovation in this field.  We believe XXX's expertise in solar technology aligns well with our goals. We would greatly value any form of support to enhance the performance of our electric vehicles, whether it is photovoltaic panels, monetary funding, or technical expertise. Collaboration with your company in our events and activities can further promote sustainable transportation solutions, which advances our shared values.  In appreciation of your support, we would like to offer the following sponsorship benefits:  Promotion of XXX on our social media and school website, highlighting your commitment to sustainability and energy efficiency. A dedicated introduction of XXX on our Instagram Stickers of the XXX logo on our project(s) Recognition at Events: During our events and competitions, XXX will be acknowledged as a major sponsor.   We believe these benefits will showcase XXXâ€™s support while also providing exposure to a community that is passionate about sustainable transportation. Please feel free to take a look at the sponsorship package as a reference for the benefits we offer! Although these benefits are offered in tiers as listed in the sponsorship package, they are flexible and we can discuss them further.  Thank you for your valuable time and consideration. I look forward to discussing this opportunity with you further. Please do not hesitate to contact me for any questions.  Best regards,  Yuqi Wang
